title: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
headline: Ending Soon: This Month’s GTA+ Benefits
content:
Thank you for being a GTA+ Member. Don’t forget to claim all of your GTA+ benefits by August 13:

— The Bravado Buffalo EVX (Muscle)
— 30% off Higgins Helitours
— The Blue Manor Hoodie and Shorts
— Double Rewards on Mr. Faber Work
— Double Rewards on Street Dealer Sales
— Light Blue Pearl Chameleon Paint
— And more

Membership renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
